---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="Research" description="Research themes in algebraic coding theory and post-quantum cryptography.">
	<section class="mt-2">
		<h1>Research</h1>
		<div class="mt-6 max-w-2xl rounded-sm border border-zinc-200/80 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
			<div class="prose max-w-none">
				<p>
					I work on (and read about) algebraic methods in coding theory and cryptography, with an emphasis on building strong
					fundamentals and writing clear expository notes.
				</p>

				<h2>Research interests</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Algebraic coding theory</strong> (algebraic and geometric structure behind codes)</li>
					<li><strong>Algebraic geometry</strong> (foundations and examples)</li>
					<li><strong>Number theory and cryptography</strong></li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Current work</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>
						Undergraduate research with
						<a href="https://mahirbilencan.github.io/">Mahir Bilen Can</a> (Tulane University)
					</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Projects, notes, and outputs</h2>
				<p>
					Selected outputs live on <a href="/work/">Work</a>. The patent-backed Anti-Chain write-up is available on
					<a href="/projects/anti-chain-posetbench/">its dedicated page</a>, and papers are listed on
					<a href="/publications/">Publications</a>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</SiteLayout>
